name: "posing for cars", 2021
description:
for a long time, this has been the sight of my tears. living under the chaotic viewpoint of São Paulo, the central region always scared me (in a good way) as a child. chaos and disorder combine with a very hard-to-accept aspect of my personality. I'm São Paulo, but is São Paulo mine? how many paths will I have to go through to say I know all the desires of this living organism?

shot on 35mm film with a Pentax IQZoom 115M.
